WEBVTT

00:00:01.856 --> 00:00:03.900
Stimulants, narcotics, cannabis.

00:00:05.110 --> 00:00:07.237
People who have used these drugs

00:00:07.320 --> 00:00:10.865
are now estimated
to total two million in Japan.

00:00:11.366 --> 00:00:14.452
The number of people arrested
for drug-related offenses

00:00:15.036 --> 00:00:17.247
is as many as 14,000 yearly.

00:00:18.706 --> 00:00:20.125
If you come any closer,

00:00:20.708 --> 00:00:22.460
I'll jump off!

00:00:22.544 --> 00:00:24.963
You're going to jump? Then get on with it.

00:00:25.046 --> 00:00:25.880
No way.

00:00:30.677 --> 00:00:31.928
Mad Dog.

00:00:32.011 --> 00:00:35.056
You're an S for the police
while being an S for the NCD.

00:00:35.140 --> 00:00:38.059
Kurosaki or me?

00:00:38.768 --> 00:00:39.769
Think hard.

00:00:39.853 --> 00:00:42.313
-I didn't do anything!
-Screw you!

00:00:42.397 --> 00:00:44.482
Even if it was against their will,

00:00:44.566 --> 00:00:48.278
once consumed, one's body
will never forget the taste of drugs.

00:00:48.361 --> 00:00:50.530
They get addicted
without even realizing it.

00:00:50.613 --> 00:00:52.615
I don't know jack about cocaine.

00:00:52.699 --> 00:00:55.034
Like hell I'm giving you my urine!

00:00:55.118 --> 00:00:59.330
You refuse to offer your urine
for testing, correct?

00:00:59.414 --> 00:01:01.040
Stay still, okay?

00:01:01.124 --> 00:01:02.959
You'll injure your urethra!

00:01:03.042 --> 00:01:04.210
No!

00:01:04.294 --> 00:01:06.254
The reason you're still here

00:01:06.337 --> 00:01:09.507
is because your father
is a senior commissioner and my superior.

00:01:10.091 --> 00:01:13.386
-I'm aware.
-Then bring me results, not words.

00:01:13.469 --> 00:01:15.138
Never lose to the NCD again.

00:01:15.221 --> 00:01:16.097
Yes, sir.

00:01:18.725 --> 00:01:19.893
What do you want?

00:01:25.189 --> 00:01:26.274
Wait, what?

00:01:43.541 --> 00:01:46.544
Your next mission is to mislead the NCD

00:01:46.628 --> 00:01:49.589
and leak information
on the cocaine supplier to me.

00:01:50.298 --> 00:01:52.634
How? Kurosaki is at the hospital, right?

00:01:53.885 --> 00:01:58.181
The NCD will be desperate to make Kaga
spill the source of his cocaine.

00:01:58.681 --> 00:02:01.059
But Kaga won't talk so easily.

00:02:01.142 --> 00:02:02.477
I bet.

00:02:02.560 --> 00:02:05.688
If he talks,
he's in for an even worse time than now.

00:02:05.772 --> 00:02:07.982
Their world isn't so simple.

00:02:09.359 --> 00:02:13.363
It's a lot like how you had to quit acting
after you got violent while drunk.

00:02:13.446 --> 00:02:14.364
Buzz off.

00:02:15.240 --> 00:02:19.452
Once Kaga gets out of prison,
he won't be able to appear on TV anymore.

00:02:19.535 --> 00:02:22.330
But at his age,
it will be hard to find other work.

00:02:22.413 --> 00:02:24.165
In order for him to survive,

00:02:24.249 --> 00:02:28.086
he'll need patrons
who help get him business.

00:02:29.128 --> 00:02:32.048
If he gives up his patrons
who supply him with cocaine

00:02:32.131 --> 00:02:35.385
and have criminal connections,
he won't live long.

00:02:36.511 --> 00:02:39.013
That is why Kaga will stay silent.

00:02:39.555 --> 00:02:43.476
This way, his patrons will help him
get more work, however small, later on.

00:02:44.811 --> 00:02:48.022
One scumbag backed by other scumbags, huh?

00:02:48.106 --> 00:02:49.816
Finding and arresting suppliers

00:02:49.899 --> 00:02:53.069
is the biggest accomplishment
for an investigative team.

00:02:53.152 --> 00:02:57.031
We can crush the entire operation
by following the trail from there.

00:02:57.824 --> 00:03:02.328
It's a much greater success
than arresting a random punk dealer.

00:03:02.412 --> 00:03:05.289
That accomplishment must fall
into the police's hands.

00:03:06.374 --> 00:03:08.876
But Kaga won't talk, right?

00:03:09.419 --> 00:03:11.963
Will the NCD get any info for me to leak?

00:03:12.755 --> 00:03:14.340
What's there for me to do?

00:03:14.424 --> 00:03:18.678
The NCD has Kurosaki, who'll use
any means to make a suspect talk.

00:03:18.761 --> 00:03:21.889
You just stay close to Kurosaki
and feed his info to me.

00:03:22.432 --> 00:03:24.475
Do that, and Kurosaki and the NCD,

00:03:24.559 --> 00:03:27.061
the police's rivals,
will lose their reputation.

00:03:27.145 --> 00:03:31.232
On the other hand, my standing
within the police will skyrocket.

00:03:32.358 --> 00:03:35.611
I thought the police
were supposed to uphold justice.

00:03:35.695 --> 00:03:38.948
Yet all you want is status
and accomplishments to your name.

00:03:39.032 --> 00:03:43.328
I'm sure it's tough to understand
for someone who threw away half his life.

00:03:43.411 --> 00:03:44.287
Geez.

00:03:44.829 --> 00:03:47.999
Both you and Kurosaki are so bizarre.

00:03:48.082 --> 00:03:49.625
Don't lump me in with him.

00:03:50.126 --> 00:03:54.172
That guy is just
a revenge-obsessed wraith.

00:03:55.298 --> 00:03:56.299
What does that mean?

00:04:00.595 --> 00:04:01.637
Wait.

00:04:02.347 --> 00:04:04.724
You're his S without
knowing anything about him?

00:04:05.266 --> 00:04:06.309
Kind of.

00:04:10.855 --> 00:04:13.775
Look, you're going to die
if you genuinely stick with him.

00:04:16.778 --> 00:04:19.739
The NCD was investigating
a case back then,

00:04:19.822 --> 00:04:22.158
but it ended up going to the police.

00:04:24.160 --> 00:04:27.080
His mother
wasn't just a regular meth addict.

00:04:28.289 --> 00:04:31.042
She had been cheating
with a yakuza guy for years.

00:04:31.125 --> 00:04:33.127
She was fed meth and forced

00:04:34.629 --> 00:04:36.422
into becoming a sex addict.

00:04:37.840 --> 00:04:38.841
Chemsex?

00:04:40.134 --> 00:04:42.136
A lot worse than that.

00:05:45.366 --> 00:05:46.659
What's that?

00:05:48.536 --> 00:05:50.705
Something that will feel even better.

00:05:54.208 --> 00:05:58.838
Kurosaki was part of an ordinary household
which fell into ruin because of meth.

00:06:00.047 --> 00:06:02.049
His mother gradually got addicted,

00:06:02.133 --> 00:06:05.011
dug into their savings,
and once the money ran out,

00:06:05.094 --> 00:06:07.513
the yakuza forced her into prostitution.

00:06:10.975 --> 00:06:15.271
The yakuza make money by feeding drugs
to housewives with that goal in mind.

00:06:15.771 --> 00:06:18.691
Any money earned from prostitution
just goes back to drugs.

00:06:18.774 --> 00:06:22.236
A never-ending cycle of misery,
just like the yakuza want.

00:06:27.325 --> 00:06:31.204
However, humans really struggle
with accepting who they become

00:06:31.287 --> 00:06:33.247
when they're at their lowest.

00:06:34.290 --> 00:06:35.249
His mother,

00:06:35.750 --> 00:06:38.211
who bought meth by selling her body,

00:06:38.294 --> 00:06:41.422
had convinced herself
that she was loved by the man.

00:06:42.006 --> 00:06:43.132
What?

00:06:44.258 --> 00:06:45.301
And then,

00:06:46.761 --> 00:06:48.512
things only got worse.

00:06:59.690 --> 00:07:01.400
Hey, stop it!

00:07:01.484 --> 00:07:03.152
Let me go!

00:07:19.418 --> 00:07:22.129
It took less than a year
for his mother to break.

00:07:22.213 --> 00:07:24.924
-How dare you steal my lover?
-Then that day came.

00:07:25.007 --> 00:07:27.176
His mother caused an incident.

00:07:29.512 --> 00:07:32.682
-You're such a pain, you damn bitch!
-Who is this hag?

00:07:32.765 --> 00:07:35.017
You're being fooled by that woman!

00:07:35.851 --> 00:07:39.188
You love me, don't you?

00:07:39.272 --> 00:07:41.357
She's my woman.

00:07:42.400 --> 00:07:44.777
You're just a way to make some cash.

00:07:45.903 --> 00:07:47.363
Gross hag.

00:07:48.447 --> 00:07:49.740
-Let's go.
-Yeah.

00:07:49.824 --> 00:07:51.409
She's so gross.

00:07:51.492 --> 00:07:52.910
Give me a break.

00:08:07.675 --> 00:08:09.010
It's your fault.

00:08:10.636 --> 00:08:12.430
It's your fault.

00:08:15.766 --> 00:08:17.101
Die.

00:08:17.184 --> 00:08:18.436
Die!

00:08:19.061 --> 00:08:20.271
Die!

00:08:20.855 --> 00:08:22.023
Die!

00:08:22.106 --> 00:08:23.024
Die!

00:08:24.066 --> 00:08:26.235
Die!

00:08:28.571 --> 00:08:31.282
Drug-induced psychosis?

00:08:31.365 --> 00:08:35.536
Afterwards, when the police went
to their residence searching for her,

00:08:36.579 --> 00:08:40.041
Kurosaki, still a middle schooler,
was standing there blankly,

00:08:40.124 --> 00:08:44.920
with his mother's corpse
hanging by a noose in front of him.

00:08:45.504 --> 00:08:46.672
Half a year later,

00:08:47.298 --> 00:08:50.676
his father, overcome with despair,
drowned himself in the sea.

00:08:52.345 --> 00:08:54.221
Meth laid waste to his family.

00:08:54.722 --> 00:08:58.601
That's why he bears
a deep hatred for drugs.

00:09:00.144 --> 00:09:01.228
To avenge his mother.

00:09:03.147 --> 00:09:05.691
Oh, hey, eat it before it burns.

00:09:08.277 --> 00:09:09.654
Is that why he…

00:09:10.237 --> 00:09:12.198
Why!

00:09:13.699 --> 00:09:15.868
Why the hell?

00:09:16.452 --> 00:09:18.871
It's just a drug addict who died.

00:09:19.372 --> 00:09:21.332
Ouch!

00:09:21.415 --> 00:09:23.584
Try saying that again.

00:09:23.668 --> 00:09:25.086
What?

00:09:25.169 --> 00:09:26.962
I'll kill you.

00:09:30.883 --> 00:09:33.719
So he's not just an asshole.

00:09:36.389 --> 00:09:38.891
I'll die before I let you off the hook.

00:09:39.642 --> 00:09:44.522
You're going to tell me in great detail
where you've been getting your cocaine.

00:09:45.231 --> 00:09:47.733
How many times do I have to tell you?

00:09:48.234 --> 00:09:49.944
I don't know anything!

00:09:50.444 --> 00:09:52.530
Nothing! Zilch--

00:09:53.823 --> 00:09:57.952
Once the urine test comes back,
it will be confirmed that you did cocaine.

00:09:59.120 --> 00:10:00.746
So what?

00:10:01.288 --> 00:10:05.668
Even if that happens, my only crimes
are possession and use of cocaine.

00:10:05.751 --> 00:10:09.630
Big deal. It's my first offense,
so I'll just get a suspended sentence.

00:10:11.340 --> 00:10:13.050
I won't let that happen.

00:10:14.093 --> 00:10:16.429
What, you're going to use violence now?

00:10:17.054 --> 00:10:19.265
I'll sue you if you get violent!

00:10:19.348 --> 00:10:23.561
What? Who's going
to get violent with whom now?

00:10:31.444 --> 00:10:32.528
You…

00:10:33.028 --> 00:10:34.822
What are you doing?

00:10:36.282 --> 00:10:38.367
That establishes assault.

00:10:38.451 --> 00:10:41.120
Possession and use
may get you a suspended sentence,

00:10:41.203 --> 00:10:44.373
but you're definitely going to prison
with assault added on top.

00:10:44.457 --> 00:10:46.667
Wait! Don't hit me anymore, Kaga!

00:10:46.751 --> 00:10:48.836
Stop! Please stop!

00:10:53.716 --> 00:10:57.219
Assault? When you're the one
hitting yourself?

00:10:57.303 --> 00:10:59.722
Like hell that will pass!

00:10:59.805 --> 00:11:02.850
I'm hitting myself? No.

00:11:02.933 --> 00:11:05.227
You're the one hitting me.

00:11:06.145 --> 00:11:09.190
You're going to frame me by doing that?

00:11:09.857 --> 00:11:13.068
Would the NCD do something that unjust?

00:11:13.152 --> 00:11:14.737
Unjust, you say?

00:11:14.820 --> 00:11:19.116
After you unjustly hurt all those women?

00:11:20.993 --> 00:11:22.828
Now then, what will you do?

00:11:23.454 --> 00:11:25.664
Keep feigning ignorance and go to prison?

00:11:25.748 --> 00:11:29.585
Or will you fess up and stay free
with just a suspended sentence?

00:11:29.668 --> 00:11:30.503
Choose.

00:11:30.586 --> 00:11:33.506
I fucking told you, I don't know anything!

00:11:33.589 --> 00:11:35.132
Get me my lawyer!

00:11:43.265 --> 00:11:45.309
The hell are you doing?

00:11:56.862 --> 00:11:59.949
And there are the fingerprints.

00:12:03.869 --> 00:12:07.957
This adds damage to property
on top of inflicting bodily injury.

00:12:09.208 --> 00:12:13.963
Even with a good lawyer, you'll get
over a year in prison for certain.

00:12:14.046 --> 00:12:17.716
Your prison life keeps
getting longer and longer.

00:12:18.300 --> 00:12:19.635
Anything goes, huh?

00:12:23.472 --> 00:12:24.682
Come on, man!

00:12:24.765 --> 00:12:27.643
Cutting my face? Have you gone insane?

00:12:28.435 --> 00:12:30.980
Are you fucking mad?

00:12:34.775 --> 00:12:36.485
Don't make me repeat myself.

00:12:36.569 --> 00:12:38.612
I have my own methods.

00:12:39.154 --> 00:12:40.406
Listen up.

00:12:40.489 --> 00:12:42.157
Even if you don't talk,

00:12:42.241 --> 00:12:44.827
we'll conduct searches
at random criminal hideouts.

00:12:44.910 --> 00:12:46.328
At each one,

00:12:46.412 --> 00:12:49.540
we'll declare that Kaga
gave up his supplier.

00:12:49.623 --> 00:12:51.458
What do you think will happen?

00:12:52.334 --> 00:12:54.253
Even if you get out of prison,

00:12:54.336 --> 00:12:57.631
do you think the criminals
will just leave you be?

00:12:58.924 --> 00:13:02.303
Is it worth going to such lengths
to protect your supplier?

00:13:02.845 --> 00:13:05.556
If they'll treat you
as a traitor either way,

00:13:05.639 --> 00:13:10.811
wouldn't it be better to at least
get the suspended sentence?

00:13:52.269 --> 00:13:55.064
KYONOSUKE UMEZAWA

00:14:46.740 --> 00:14:48.117
What?

00:14:48.951 --> 00:14:50.577
You're terrifying.

00:14:50.661 --> 00:14:53.080
Kaga gave up his cocaine supplier.

00:14:53.163 --> 00:14:54.999
And you just start talking?

00:14:55.082 --> 00:14:58.168
His supplier is a guy named Nagata.

00:14:59.128 --> 00:15:01.755
He's a patron and a partner
in his nightly activities.

00:15:01.839 --> 00:15:05.426
To cover his tracks,
Kaga didn't buy directly from a dealer,

00:15:05.509 --> 00:15:08.095
he bought it through Nagata instead.

00:15:08.178 --> 00:15:10.723
Nagata is the CEO of a food company.

00:15:10.806 --> 00:15:14.101
The NCD has marked him as our next target.

00:15:15.436 --> 00:15:17.730
Isn't that classified information?

00:15:18.230 --> 00:15:19.773
Should you be telling me?

00:15:20.649 --> 00:15:23.694
You fulfilled your role as an S last time.

00:15:23.777 --> 00:15:26.739
That's why I've decided to trust you.

00:15:28.073 --> 00:15:30.117
I have your trust all of a sudden?

00:15:30.200 --> 00:15:31.410
Kind of gross.

00:15:31.493 --> 00:15:34.413
This case doesn't end
with just arresting Kaga.

00:15:34.496 --> 00:15:38.792
It only ends when we uncover
and destroy the source of the drugs.

00:15:38.876 --> 00:15:41.712
That's why I want your cooperation again.

00:15:43.005 --> 00:15:44.339
What do I have to do?

00:15:44.423 --> 00:15:46.175
Back at HQ,

00:15:46.258 --> 00:15:50.721
they're looking into the suspect first
before they decide on a course of action.

00:15:50.804 --> 00:15:53.891
So no specific instructions
until they finish that?

00:15:53.974 --> 00:15:56.935
That will be too slow.
We're fighting against time.

00:15:57.603 --> 00:16:02.733
You'll go sell tons of drugs
to crooks connected to Kaga.

00:16:02.816 --> 00:16:05.152
What? To first-time customers?

00:16:05.235 --> 00:16:08.238
They'll be super suspicious
if I sell a large amount!

00:16:08.322 --> 00:16:09.406
I bet they will.

00:16:09.490 --> 00:16:11.033
-Then why?
-Because…

00:16:11.116 --> 00:16:14.953
If you sell the drugs at a lower price
compared to the market rate,

00:16:15.037 --> 00:16:17.956
the crooks will say this to their dealers,

00:16:18.040 --> 00:16:21.460
"I know a cheaper way to buy the drugs."

00:16:22.002 --> 00:16:23.420
What will happen then?

00:16:24.004 --> 00:16:25.506
If I did that,

00:16:25.589 --> 00:16:29.885
the traffickers would come and kill me
so they can protect their own profits.

00:16:29.968 --> 00:16:32.763
-Which is where we'll arrest them!
-Hang on a second!

00:16:32.846 --> 00:16:34.890
-What?
-Don't give me that.

00:16:34.973 --> 00:16:37.684
They'll go after my life.
I could get killed!

00:16:37.768 --> 00:16:40.062
It's fine. We'll catch them before that.

00:16:41.313 --> 00:16:43.065
What if I die?

00:16:45.526 --> 00:16:46.401
Don't.

00:16:46.485 --> 00:16:47.986
Don't make it sound simple!

00:16:48.570 --> 00:16:50.447
That's too dangerous for me.

00:16:50.531 --> 00:16:53.367
I told you I decided to trust you.

00:16:53.867 --> 00:16:54.952
Yeah, don't.

00:16:55.035 --> 00:16:57.454
Just do it. I'll arrest you if you don't.

00:16:59.123 --> 00:17:00.791
We're back to that again?

00:17:01.708 --> 00:17:04.670
Also, what became of Aoi Sugihara?

00:17:06.004 --> 00:17:08.048
I've called her over ten times.

00:17:12.469 --> 00:17:14.138
SHIKAWAHANACHO

00:17:14.221 --> 00:17:16.473
She's at home. Go check on her.

00:17:20.936 --> 00:17:25.315
So Kurosaki made Kaga confess
and cooked up that whole plan?

00:17:26.650 --> 00:17:28.569
What a crafty bastard.

00:17:28.652 --> 00:17:30.529
So what should I do?

00:17:31.029 --> 00:17:33.866
Pretend to agree
to Kurosaki's offer and buy time.

00:17:34.366 --> 00:17:35.242
What?

00:17:35.325 --> 00:17:39.204
At this rate, the NCD might
get the jump on us again.

00:17:39.288 --> 00:17:41.999
Yeah, okay, whatever you say.

00:17:49.882 --> 00:17:51.425
The report on Noriaki Nagata.

00:17:58.390 --> 00:17:59.433
Quick work.

00:17:59.933 --> 00:18:01.101
Thank you.

00:18:01.602 --> 00:18:04.229
We ran an inquiry
for Noriaki Nagata in the database

00:18:04.313 --> 00:18:07.274
and learned that Nagata
is connected to the Saeki Family,

00:18:07.357 --> 00:18:09.401
which the outlaw Matsubara works for.

00:18:10.235 --> 00:18:14.323
We believe Nagata purchased cocaine
from the Saeki Family.

00:18:15.908 --> 00:18:17.242
Nagata.

00:18:20.871 --> 00:18:22.915
Never mind small fry like him.

00:18:23.498 --> 00:18:27.836
I don't know where the punk is from,
but I doubt he's even alive anymore.

00:18:28.337 --> 00:18:29.171
Sir.

00:18:30.547 --> 00:18:32.591
Focus on the Saeki Family.

00:18:33.342 --> 00:18:34.676
To be clear,

00:18:34.760 --> 00:18:38.847
I want you to use whatever means it takes
to get them before the NCD.

00:20:07.311 --> 00:20:08.353
Ow!

00:20:09.146 --> 00:20:10.981
Shit.

00:20:13.108 --> 00:20:14.318
Stop right there!

00:20:16.570 --> 00:20:18.030
Are you Aoi Sugihara?

00:20:19.364 --> 00:20:21.408
I'm Kurosaki, a narcotics agent.

00:20:31.043 --> 00:20:31.877
What is this?

00:20:35.797 --> 00:20:36.798
It's…

00:20:37.299 --> 00:20:38.425
Hey, wait!

00:20:41.219 --> 00:20:42.763
What are you doing?

00:20:42.846 --> 00:20:44.473
Isn't she a victim?

00:20:47.225 --> 00:20:48.518
Is that…

00:20:52.981 --> 00:20:53.815
It can't be.

00:20:54.983 --> 00:20:56.485
There has to be a mistake.

00:20:58.528 --> 00:20:59.654
Answer me.

00:21:00.155 --> 00:21:01.823
This isn't yours, right?!

00:21:08.497 --> 00:21:09.539
Let's go.

00:21:09.623 --> 00:21:10.540
Wait!

00:21:11.625 --> 00:21:14.419
She wouldn't have done this
if Kaga hadn't drugged her with cocaine!

00:21:15.003 --> 00:21:16.588
She's a victim! So why--

00:21:16.671 --> 00:21:19.841
She's no longer a victim
if she buys cocaine herself!

00:21:20.592 --> 00:21:23.095
We have a responsibility to arrest her.

00:21:23.720 --> 00:21:25.138
You're a dealer.

00:21:25.222 --> 00:21:28.350
You should already know
the hell that awaits her.

00:21:29.601 --> 00:21:31.061
I said, wait!

00:21:39.403 --> 00:21:40.987
What are you doing?

00:21:41.988 --> 00:21:43.365
You can't.

00:21:45.242 --> 00:21:46.993
Even if it's hard or tough.

00:21:47.911 --> 00:21:50.163
You have to endure it.

00:21:51.790 --> 00:21:56.670
I said you would hurt those dear to you
and lose everything if you did drugs.

00:21:59.464 --> 00:22:00.715
So why?

00:22:03.927 --> 00:22:06.346
Please, come to your senses!

00:22:06.430 --> 00:22:08.974
That man is just preying on you!

00:22:09.057 --> 00:22:10.100
No!

00:22:10.183 --> 00:22:12.060
We love each other!

00:22:12.144 --> 00:22:16.356
He wouldn't make you take drugs
and sell your body if he loved you!

00:22:16.440 --> 00:22:18.400
This is how they exploit people!

00:22:18.483 --> 00:22:21.403
Wrong! You're wrong!

00:22:22.612 --> 00:22:24.448
Please, I want a divorce.

00:22:25.157 --> 00:22:26.950
Let me be free!

00:22:27.033 --> 00:22:29.202
You can have Toru.

00:22:29.286 --> 00:22:30.328
So please!

00:22:34.624 --> 00:22:36.918
Please. I'm begging you.

00:22:37.002 --> 00:22:39.337
Come back to your senses.

00:22:42.465 --> 00:22:45.552
Please, just come back
to your senses, you idiot!

00:23:06.364 --> 00:23:08.825
I'm sorry! Mercy, please!

00:23:08.909 --> 00:23:10.869
I promise I won't say anything!

00:23:10.952 --> 00:23:13.330
I won't tell a soul
that I bought from the Saeki Family!

00:23:13.914 --> 00:23:16.499
Please, have mercy on me!

00:23:25.634 --> 00:23:27.677
How about we go for an eyeball?

00:23:28.178 --> 00:23:29.471
Don't!

00:23:29.554 --> 00:23:32.933
The Saeki Family that has been looking
after us needs some more manpower.

00:23:33.016 --> 00:23:36.519
One look at how they clean
and I can tell if they're useful.

00:23:36.603 --> 00:23:38.855
If they seem trustworthy,
they'll get the goods.

00:23:39.356 --> 00:23:42.901
If I infiltrate it, we can grasp
the entire flow of the cocaine.

00:23:42.984 --> 00:23:44.110
With this plan,

00:23:44.194 --> 00:23:48.114
we can get more than just the people
who directly sold the cocaine to Nagata.

00:23:48.198 --> 00:23:49.574
The client list.

00:23:49.658 --> 00:23:52.702
Search for it. Find it. Bring it to me.
That's the condition.

00:23:52.786 --> 00:23:54.287
All right.

00:23:55.038 --> 00:24:00.961
ANY RESEMBLANCE TO ACTUAL PERSONS,
GROUPS, OR CASES IS PURELY COINCIDENTAL

00:24:01.044 --> 00:24:02.003
Subtitle translation by: Saim Ul Hassan